# Vehicle spec + AI enrichment

Before building vehicle-spec UI or AI parse→enrich flows, read:

**`agents/ShopRallyCRM/VEHICLE-SPEC-AI-MEMORY.md`**

Key rules:
- **Do not require VIN** to show or enrich specs — YMM (+ trim/engine) is enough to start; VIN improves accuracy.
- Hybrid: AI parse → EPA/NHTSA catalog → optional VIN decode → MOTOR when licensed.
- Tekmetric = right-rail accordion (Vehicle + Fluids…); AutoLeap = header info modal for fluids/battery.
